|2 |  └─SORT                           |               |2       |11          |
|3 |    └─UNION ALL                    |               |2       |11          |
|4 |      ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |               |1       |6           |
|5 |      │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t1             |1       |3           |
|6 |      │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t2             |1       |3           |
|7 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |               |1       |6           |
|8 |        ├─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t2             |1       |3           |
|9 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t1             |0       |3           |
==============================================================================
